<pb n="0052a" xml:id="I01.0019.0052a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0052a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 19</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0052a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>錡雙胡廿人等造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0052a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陽</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陽</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0052a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0052a0101">富平令王承祖　但官錡眾<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">舉</unclear>　平望田安周　邑子錡陽生
<lb ed="I" n="0052a02" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　侍者錡石珍　平望錡神裕　邑子錡景略
<lb ed="I" n="0052a03" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　　　　　但官錡思山　邑子錡神歡
<lb ed="I" n="0052a04" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　　　　　邑正錡平洛　邑子錡虎略
<lb ed="I" n="0052a05" type="honorific"/>邑師錡雙胡　　侍者錡舉　　邑正王買興</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0052b00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之二　碑陰</cb:mulu><head>之二　碑陰</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0052b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0052b0101">典坐錡道憘
<lb ed="I" n="0052b02" type="honorific"/>典錄錡承祖　邑子錡馬仁
<lb ed="I" n="0052b03" type="honorific"/>邑子錡申起　香火錡神敬
<lb ed="I" n="0052b04" type="honorific"/>典錄錡歡洛</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0052c00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之三　碑側</cb:mulu><head>之三　碑側</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0052c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0052c0101">□□□□□先<note n="0052001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">刼＝劫【史】</note><note n="0052001" resp="ihp" type="mod">刼【佛拓】，劫【史】</note><app n="0052001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">劫</lem><rdg wit="【原】">刼</rdg></app>以<note n="0052002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30460"/>＝來【史】</note><note n="0052002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30460"/>【佛拓】，來【史】</note><app n="0052002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">來</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30460"/></rdg></app>。應形化世。靜志靈<note n="0052003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30452"/>＝淵【史】</note><note n="0052003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30452"/>【佛拓】，淵【史】</note><app n="0052003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30452"/></rdg></app>。清脩万行。乃運窮通。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">濁</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">明</unclear>□
<lb ed="I" n="0052c02" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">三</unclear>□□□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">世</unclear>之常。事<note n="0052004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30453"/>＝體【史】</note><note n="0052004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30453"/>【佛拓】，體【史】</note><app n="0052004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">體</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30453"/></rdg></app>真極之妙。嘗獲无為以自安。控玄範以騰覩。馳<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">逸</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0052c03" type="honorific"/>万□。人天蒙<note n="0052005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30454"/>＝慶【史】</note><note n="0052005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30454"/>【佛拓】，慶【史】</note><app n="0052005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">慶</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30454"/></rdg></app>。感緣既周。凝神靜<note n="0052006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30351"/>＝樂【史】</note><note n="0052006" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30351"/>【佛拓】，樂【史】</note><app n="0052006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">樂</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30351"/></rdg></app>。真容雖遷。像化<note n="0052007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢏏＝彌【史】</note><note n="0052007" resp="ihp" type="mod">𢏏【佛拓】，彌【史】</note><app n="0052007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">彌</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢏏</rdg></app>振。然今千載之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">下</unclear>。
<lb ed="I" n="0052c04" type="honorific"/>合邑廿人等。覺世非常。捨己名珍。為國為家。造石像一軀。彫<note n="0052008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">尅＝剋【史】</note><note n="0052008" resp="ihp" type="mod">尅【佛拓】，剋【史】</note><app n="0052008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">尅</rdg></app><note n="0052009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30459"/>＝成【史】</note><note n="0052009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30459"/>【佛拓】，成【史】</note><app n="0052009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">成</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30459"/></rdg></app><note n="0052010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30455"/>＝就【史】</note><note n="0052010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30455"/>【佛拓】，就【史】</note><app n="0052010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">就</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30455"/></rdg></app>。寫真
<lb ed="I" n="0052c05" type="honorific"/>容<note n="0052011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">业＝止【史】</note><note n="0052011" resp="ihp" type="mod">业【佛拓】，止【史】</note><app n="0052011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">止</lem><rdg wit="【原】">业</rdg></app>。應安處路衝。高平<note n="0052012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30456"/>＝顯【史】</note><note n="0052012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30456"/>【佛拓】，顯【史】</note><app n="0052012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顯</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30456"/></rdg></app>唱。討邑恭養。隨時不闕。以是造像功德。上願皇
<lb ed="I" n="0052c06" type="honorific"/>□陛下紹隆万劫。匡<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">拯</unclear>三寶。千載不隧。下願合邑亡過師尊父母。長志天
<lb ed="I" n="0052c07" type="honorific"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">闕</unclear>。託化紫蓮。栖神万法。<note n="0052013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">逯＝逮【史】</note><note n="0052013" resp="ihp" type="mod">逯【佛拓】，逮【史】</note><app n="0052013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">逮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">逯</rdg></app>及合邑。三界六趣。咸同斯<app type="star" corresp="#0052005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">慶</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30454"/></rdg></app>。<note n="0052014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30457"/>＝業【史】</note><note n="0052014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30457"/>【佛拓】，業【史】</note><app n="0052014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">業</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30457"/></rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0052009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">成</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30459"/></rdg></app>真道。
<lb ed="I" n="0052c08" type="honorific"/>大□神龜三年歲次庚子年四月甲辰<note n="0052015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30458"/>＝朔【史】</note><note n="0052015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30458"/>【佛拓】，朔【史】</note><app n="0052015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朔</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30458"/></rdg></app>八日造訖。</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
